  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      TJ-100, a Japanese herbal medicine, is clinically effective in postoperative ileus. So it may
      activate bowel movement. This study will test the efficacy and safety of TJ-100 in the
      treatment of patients with chronic constipation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
