  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  chronic constipation defined as less than 3 spontaneous bowel movement frequencies per
             week

          -  had symptoms of abdominal bloating or discomfort

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  mechanical bowel obstruction

          -  clinically systemic disease-induced constipation

          -  pregnancy
      </textblock>
